OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening and night with outbreaks of
OL,7,Frain, this heaviest and most
OL,8,Fpersistent across the south. Turning
OL,9,Fdrier with a few coastal showers
OL,10,Flater. Strong to gale southerly winds
OL,11,Falong the west coast this evening.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FA mainly dry day with some
OL,14,Fsunny spells. A few showers along the
OL,15,Fwest coast at first, and again later
OL,16,Fin the afternoon. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
