OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FTuesday and Wednesday begin frosty but
OL,7,Fstay dry and sunny. The wind will
OL,8,Fstrengthen on Thursday when outbreaks
OL,9,Fof rain spread east.
